{"tid":1645541,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助]Telegram及「連登仔方法」到底係咩","createTime":"2019-10-11T02:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T13:02:16.000Z","uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3bedbd64954645d0f882a3dc2faa89627002fb59","tid":1645541,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我打算join個幫人補習group，反正我未搵到工，大把時間<br />\n個group係 你發夢 我補習<br />\n<br />\n個group有一段要求係咁的：<br />\n為確保義補的質素，請提供公開試的照片證明（用連登仔方法：自貼Tg user name + 證書），不用展示個人資料或名字。<br />\n<br />\n請問即係點？因為我唔識用telegram。所以我想問：<br />\n(1) 『自貼Tg user name』我估應係，開telegram後，畫面左上方有一格三橫線的，按佢，就會見到自己個名及電話號碼。我估應該係咁？<br />\n(2) 如的確係咁，我又駛唔駛改圖遮左自己個電話號碼先？ (抑或此舉係多餘？)<br />\n(3) 然後我該點send/send 去邊？用e-mail send？抑或telegram reply message咁樣send？<br />\n<br />\n求幫忙！   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e540754b63a7498ed25057f03f20aa07204b6750","tid":1645541,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44234b13381886f922cd9b1dda29b92eefb06bb1","tid":1645541,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d491ac97d3f2b6cdea8a389e1eaa18036a9a108","tid":1645541,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afea469c4736d2c854ba9d1aa5a7d583701c471","tid":1645541,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bf8e60083b270d436fd0351009df51189e1bed","tid":1645541,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face